{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/timevalprotocol\/toiso8601()"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"toIso8601"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String"},{"kind":"text","text":"!"}],"modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"title":"toIso8601()","externalID":"s:4GLib15TimeValProtocolPAAE9toIso8601SSSgyF","extendedModule":"GLib","roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","platforms":[]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/TimeValProtocol\/toIso8601()"},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"abstract":[{"text":"Converts ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"time"},{"text":" into an RFC 3339 encoded string, relative to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Coordinated Universal Time (UTC). This is one of the many formats","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"allowed by ISO 8601."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"toIso8601","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"kind":"text","text":"!"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"ISO 8601 allows a large number of date\/time formats, with or without"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"punctuation and optional elements. The format returned by this function"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is a complete date and time, with optional punctuation included, the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"UTC time zone represented as “Z”, and the "},{"code":"tv_usec","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" part included if"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and only if it is nonzero, i.e. either","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"“YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ” or “YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SS.fffffZ”."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This corresponds to the Internet date\/time format defined by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/www.ietf.org\/rfc\/rfc3339.txt","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and to either of the two most-precise formats defined by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the W3C Note"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/TR\/NOTE-datetime-19980827","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Both of these documents are profiles of ISO 8601."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_date_time_format()"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"code":"g_strdup_printf()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if a different"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"variation of ISO 8601 format is required."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"code":"time","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" represents a date which is too large to fit into a "},{"code":"struct tm","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":" will be returned. This is platform dependent. Note also that since","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"GTimeVal","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" stores the number of seconds as a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"glong"},{"text":", on 32-bit systems it","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"is subject to the year 2038 problem. Accordingly, since GLib 2.62, this"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"function has been deprecated. Equivalent functionality is available using:"}]},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":["GDateTime *dt = g_date_time_new_from_unix_utc (time_val);","iso8601_string = g_date_time_format_iso8601 (dt);","g_date_time_unref (dt);"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The return value of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_time_val_to_iso8601()"},{"type":"text","text":" has been nullable since GLib"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"2.54; before then, GLib would crash under the same conditions.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"to_iso8601 is deprecated:"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"#GTimeVal is not year-2038-safe. Use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"g_date_time_format_iso8601(dt) instead."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/TimeValProtocol"]]},"references":{"https://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc3339.txt":{"identifier":"https:\/\/www.ietf.org\/rfc\/rfc3339.txt","title":"RFC 3339","url":"https:\/\/www.ietf.org\/rfc\/rfc3339.txt","type":"link","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"RFC 3339"}]},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/TimeValProtocol":{"url":"\/documentation\/glib\/timevalprotocol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"TimeValProtocol","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"TimeValProtocol"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/TimeValProtocol","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","title":"TimeValProtocol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Represents a precise time, with seconds and microseconds."}]},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","title":"GLib","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/glib","abstract":[]},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/TimeValProtocol/toIso8601()":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/TimeValProtocol\/toIso8601()","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Converts "},{"code":"time","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" into an RFC 3339 encoded string, relative to the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Coordinated Universal Time (UTC). This is one of the many formats"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"allowed by ISO 8601.","type":"text"}],"deprecated":true,"url":"\/documentation\/glib\/timevalprotocol\/toiso8601()","kind":"symbol","title":"toIso8601()","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"toIso8601","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"() -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String"},{"text":"!","kind":"text"}]},"http://www.w3.org/TR/NOTE-datetime-19980827":{"identifier":"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/TR\/NOTE-datetime-19980827","title":"Date and Time Formats","url":"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/TR\/NOTE-datetime-19980827","type":"link","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Date and Time Formats"}]}}}